sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as RagasEvaluatorInline<br/>(in-process)
    participant Remote as RagasEvaluatorRemote<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation

    Client->>LS: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LS->>Inline: Route to inline::trustyai_ragas
    Inline->>LS: Read dataset (DatasetIO API)<br/>in-process Python call
    LS-->>Inline: Dataset rows
    Inline->>LS: LLM inference (Inference API)<br/>in-process via LlamaStackInlineLLM
    LS-->>Inline: LLM response
    Inline->>LS: Embeddings (Inference API)<br/>in-process via LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings
    LS-->>Inline: Embedding vectors
    Note over Inline: ragas.evaluate() runs<br/>in asyncio.to_thread
    Inline-->>LS: Evaluation results
    Client->>LS: GET /alpha/eval/job/result<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LS-->>Client: JSON evaluation results

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)

    Client->>LS: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LS->>Remote: Route to remote::trustyai_ragas
    Remote->>KFP: GET /apis/v2beta1/healthz<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: Health OK
    Remote->>KFP: create_run_from_pipeline_func<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Bearer Token
    KFP-->>Remote: Run ID

    Note over KFP,KFPPod: KFP executes 2-step pipeline

    KFP->>KFPPod: Step 1: retrieve_data
    KFPPod->>LS: GET datasets<br/>8321/TCP HTTP (no auth)
    LS-->>KFPPod: Dataset rows
    KFP->>KFPPod: Step 2: run_ragas
    KFPPod->>LS: LLM inference<br/>8321/TCP HTTP via LlamaStackRemoteLLM
    LS-->>KFPPod: LLM response
    KFPPod->>LS: Embeddings<br/>8321/TCP HTTP via LlamaStackRemoteEmbeddings
    LS-->>KFPPod: Embedding vectors
    Note over KFPPod: ragas.evaluate() runs
    KFPPod->>S3: Write results (JSONL)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS AWS IAM
    S3-->>KFPPod: Write confirmed

    Client->>LS: GET /alpha/eval/job/status<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    Remote->>KFP: Check run status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    KFP-->>Remote: Run completed
    Remote->>S3: Fetch results (s3fs)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS AWS IAM
    S3-->>Remote: JSONL results
    LS-->>Client: JSON evaluation results
